                            <outline text="Motivation #slide ">
<outline text="Focus on first and second game"/>
<outline text="This avoids third, which is less interesting from GT point of view and also could be avoided through proper vetting "/>
<outline text="Strategies are effectively: cooperate, not cooperate and trust, not trust"/>
<outline text="Denoted as $$\{C, \bar{C}\}$$ and  $$\{T, \bar{T}\}$$. "/>
