                        <outline text="Paper 3: Mohebbi Moghaddam M., Manshaei M.H., Zhu Q. (2015) To Trust or Not: A Security Signaling Game Between Service Provider and Client. In: Panaousis E. et al ed., Decision and Game Theory for Security. GameSec 2015. [cited: 6]"/>
